'''Whippendell Woods''' is located near the town of [[Wikipedia:Watford|Watford]] in England. It was used for two short sequences in [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']]: the opening scenes on [[Naboo]] with [[Qui-Gon Jinn]] and [[Obi-Wan Kenobi]] when they first meet [[Jar Jar Binks]], and the [[Gungan Sacred Place/Legends|Gungan Sacred Place]].

